#originalTopic=does-owning-a-gun-make-you-safer
Families in Iraq were allowed to keep an AK and one clip.  These are highly effective against a jihaddist with three 110 mm rounds wrapped in det cord in his white Opal, driving around to find something he didn't like so he could spark the cord and eliminate the target and himself.  Dogs were all over the place there; a shout seemed as effective against them as the report of a rifle.  